<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>주문하기</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/order.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

        <main class="container page">
            <section class="page-title-wrap">
                <h2 class="page-title">주문하기</h2>
                <p class="page-desc">주문 정보를 확인하고 결제를 진행하세요.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="order-layout">
                <div class="order-main">
                    <section class="order-box">
                        <h3 class="order-box-title">주문 상품</h3>
                        <div id="order-products-box">
                            <p class="empty-message">주문 상품을 불러오는 중입니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="order-box">
                        <h3 class="order-box-title">주문자 정보</h3>

                        <div class="member-order-notice" id="member-order-notice" hidden>
                            로그인 회원 주문입니다. 회원 계정 기준으로 주문이 진행됩니다.
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-grid" id="guest-order-form">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="order-name">이름</label>
                                <input type="text" id="order-name" placeholder="이름을 입력하세요" />
                            </div>

                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="order-email">이메일</label>
                                <input type="email" id="order-email" placeholder="이메일을 입력하세요" />
                            </div>

                            <div class="form-group full">
                                <label for="order-phone">연락처</label>
                                <input type="text" id="order-phone" placeholder="연락처를 입력하세요" />
                            </div>

                            <div class="form-group full">
                                <label for="order-password">주문조회 비밀번호</label>
                                <input type="password" id="order-password" placeholder="비회원 주문조회용 비밀번호를 입력하세요" />
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="order-box">
                        <h3 class="order-box-title">결제 수단</h3>

                        <div class="payment-options">
                            <label class="payment-option">
                                <input type="radio" name="payment" value="card" checked />
                                <span>신용카드</span>
                            </label>

                            <label class="payment-option">
                                <input type="radio" name="payment" value="bank" />
                                <span>계좌이체</span>
                            </label>

                            <label class="payment-option">
                                <input type="radio" name="payment" value="simple" />
                                <span>간편결제</span>
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                </div>

                <aside class="order-summary">
                    <h3 class="summary-title">결제 정보</h3>

                    <ul class="summary-list">
                        <li>
                            <span>상품 금액</span>
                            <strong id="order-product-price">0원</strong>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span>할인 금액</span>
                            <strong>0원</strong>
                        </li>
                        <li class="summary-total">
                            <span>총 결제 금액</span>
                            <strong id="order-total-price">0원</strong>
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary summary-btn" id="complete-order-btn">결제 완료하기</button>
                    <a href="/cart-page" class="btn btn-outline summary-btn">장바구니로 돌아가기</a>
                </aside>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
            <script src="/js/order.js"></script>
            <script src="/js/common.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
